---
// Standalone 404 — noindex (Base.astro hard-codes index,follow, so this page renders its own shell)
---
<html lang="en" class="grain">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Page not found — The Yanuka, in English</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, follow" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml" />
    <style>
      :root{--g:#0a0e1a;--gold:#d8b976;--goldb:#f0d99a;--ink:#e8e4da;--soft:#a9a294;--line:rgba(216,185,118,.16)}
      *{margin:0;box-sizing:border-box}
      body{background:var(--g);color:var(--ink);font:16px/1.65 Assistant,system-ui,sans-serif;min-height:100vh;display:grid;place-items:center;text-align:center;padding:24px}
      h1{font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:clamp(2rem,6vw,3.2rem);color:var(--goldb);margin-bottom:10px}
      p{color:var(--soft);max-width:460px;margin:0 auto 26px}
      a.b{display:inline-block;padding:.65em 1.5em;border-radius:999px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;margin:4px}
      a.g{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--goldb),var(--gold));color:#23180a}
      a.o{border:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--goldb)}
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <img src="/favicon.svg" alt="" width="56" height="56" />
      <h1>This page isn't here</h1>
      <p>The page you were looking for doesn't exist — but every shiur, niggun and alon of the Yanuka is one tap away.</p>
      <div>
        <a class="b g" href="/">Go to the homepage</a>
        <a class="b o" href="/torah/">Browse the Torah Library</a>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
